Package: ImageMetrologyAnalysis
Type: Package
Title: High-Performance Numerical Routines for Microscopic/Metrological Image ANanlysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Chitran", "Ghosal",
      email = "ghosal.chitran@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides high-performance numerical routines with R and Fortran backends
    for the analysis of microscopic and metrological images. Includes tools for
    image preprocessing, FFT-based filtering, quantitative surface statistics,
    and data visualization to support advanced metrology and materials research.
